      • createViewItems

        public static java.util.List<javax.swing.JMenuItem> createViewItems​(PlatformDefinition platform,
                                                                    CalcServerRequester requester,
                                                                    Job job,
                                                                    ViewableFile[] files)
        Returns a list of menus and menu items that contain one item for each viewable file organized into sub-menus based on their broad category as defined in FileTypeCategory.
        Parameters:
        platform - the PlatformDefinition that contains the job
        requester - the CalcServerRequester to request from
        job - the Job that contains the files
        files - a ViewableFile[] describing the files for which items should be created
        Returns:
        a list of sub-menus that contain items for each of the broadly supported document types found in FileTypeCategory
        See Also:
        FileTypeCategory
